## Enviroment File

```bash

PORT=8080
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://postgres:password@localhost:5432/OneTure"

```

## Installation

```bash

$ npm install
$ npm install -g typescript

```

## Prisma
# Make Sure you have postgreSQL

# generate Prisma client(when prisma model update run below command or after initial project setup)

```bash

$ npx prisma generate

```

# run below command db migration(It will update/create db inside postgresql )

```bash

$ npx prisma db push

```

## Running the app in dev mode

```bash

$ npm run dev

```

## Running the app on production

```bash
$ npm run build
$ npm start

```